item.title: ResNet Overview and Implementatoin
item.author: sciredomir@tutanota.com (Mahan)
item.description: ResNet model and the seminal paper, Deep Residual Learning for Image Recognition by Kaiming He, Xiangyu Zhang, Shaoqing Ren, and Jian Sun, which won the Best Paper award at CVPR 2016. It is one of the most influential and fundamental papers in the history of deep learning for computer vision.
